org.activebpel.rt.bpel.coord

Packages that use org.activebpel.rt.bpel.coord
org.activebpel.rt.bpel.coord This package contains the base classes for implementing coordination. 
org.activebpel.rt.bpel.impl This package contains the base classes used in the implementation model for the BPEL activities. 
org.activebpel.rt.bpel.impl.activity.support Includes supporting bpel objects which aren't properly activities.  
org.activebpel.rt.bpel.server.admin Classes that manage queued receives and a bean that holds deployed process information.

org.activebpel.rt.bpel.server.coord.state

org.activebpel.rt.bpel.server.engine The BPEL engine, support classes, and engine factory.  
org.activebpel.rt.bpel.server.engine.storage This package contains classes for storing the state of BPEL processes to an external storage facility. 
org.activebpel.rt.bpel.server.engine.storage.providers   
org.activebpel.rt.bpel.server.engine.storage.sql This package contains classes for storing the state of BPEL processes to a SQL database. 
org.activebpel.rt.bpel.server.engine.storage.sql.handlers This package contains ResultSet handlers for SQL queries used by the classes in the org.activebpel.rt.bpel.server.engine.storage.sql package.

org.activebpel.rt.bpel.server.engine.storage.xmldb.coord.handlers

Classes in org.activebpel.rt.bpel.coord used by org.activebpel.rt.bpel.coord
AeCoordinationDetail
          Contains instance information about a coordination.
AeCoordinationException
          Base class for coordination related exceptions.
AeCoordinationNotFoundException
          Exception to indicate a coordination or context was not found in the server.
IAeCoordinating
          Defines an activity that is either the coordinator or the participant (coordinatable).
IAeCoordinationContext
          Interface for a WS-Coordination context.
IAeCoordinator
          Defines the interface for object that acts as the coordinator.
IAeCreateContextRequest
          Interface for a WS-Coordination CreateCoordinationContext Note: This is an internal implementation tailored to be used with requirement 111 ie - the interface provides a simple property getter and setter.
IAeCreateContextResponse
          Interface for a WS-Coordination CreateCoordinationContextResponse Note: This is an internal implementation tailored to be used with requirement 111 ie - the interface provides a simple property getter and setter.
IAeParticipant
          Interface to indicate the participant in a coordinated activity.
IAeProtocolMessage
          Interface for a WS-Coordination protocol message that is exchanged between the coordinator and the participant.
IAeProtocolState
          Interface to indicate WS-Coordination protocol state.
IAeRegistrationRequest
          Interface for a WS-Coordination registation request.
IAeRegistrationResponse
          Interface for a WS-Coordination registation response.
